Miguel Roldán, Daniel Mòdol and Marta Bayona: the contest is timely.
For Roldan, after addressing the coastal front "it is necessary" to debate "the mountain front," since the speech of Ildefons Cerdà, that of green apples, has not been carried out.
"It is possible to start from the base that the most extensive park in Barcelona is the beach.
